151
00:09:40,958 --> 00:09:42,041
‪Ta đều vậy chứ?

152
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:44,375
‪Giơ tay tôi xem.

153
00:09:44,833 --> 00:09:46,083
‪Tay tôi đang cầm hộp.

154
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:49,625
